00:03:14,850 --> 00:03:15,730
Just be quick.

18
00:03:16,020 --> 00:03:16,660
Tell us.

19
00:03:16,660 --> 00:03:17,579
How did the birthday go?

20
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:18,140
Nothing happened.

21
00:03:19,060 --> 00:03:19,660
Nothing happened?

22
00:03:21,010 --> 00:03:21,940
What did you do then?

23
00:03:22,140 --> 00:03:22,650
I broke up with her.

24
