27
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:33,890
Did Mingming say that to you?

28
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:35,970
Don't look at me like that.

29
00:03:35,970 --> 00:03:37,340
It sounds like something Mingming would say.

30
00:03:38,140 --> 00:03:39,300
You are my friends.

31
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:40,340
I know you too well.

32
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:41,300
Moreover,

33
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:42,690
only Qin Mingming will say those things to you.

34
00:03:44,329 --> 00:03:46,460
You've got your own problem,

35
00:03:46,940 --> 00:03:47,820
but what has happened

36
00:03:47,820 --> 00:03:50,100
was not caused by you only.

37
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:51,460
Don't get too upset.

38
00:03:53,060 --> 00:03:54,660
I think that

39
00:03:54,940 --> 00:03:56,740
Lulu may not be the best for you.

40
00:03:59,780 --> 00:04:00,580
Don't dwell on that.

41
00:04:00,620 --> 00:04:01,780
There is no right or wrong in relationships.

42
00:04:02,050 --> 00:04:02,930
You've missed this.

43
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:04,940
Seize the next one.

44
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:09,460
Just work hard and get distracted.

45
00:04:10,410 --> 00:04:11,820
You just want me

46
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:13,100
to help with packing.

47
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:14,170
Xu Zihao,

48
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:16,100
