49
00:04:16,690 --> 00:04:17,339
I have faith in you.

50
00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:18,060
Work.

51
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:19,540
Sadness can be your power.

52
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:22,140
