56
00:04:28,180 --> 00:04:28,860
What?

57
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:30,820
One day later and you two are together now?

58
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:33,940
Xiao Xiu and I,

59
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:35,850
we are dating.

60
00:04:36,730 --> 00:04:37,260
A while ago,

61
00:04:37,260 --> 00:04:38,780
something was wrong with my family.

62
00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:40,570
It's hard to explain.

63
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:41,700
More importantly,

64
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:43,540
I can remember everything now.

65
00:04:43,980 --> 00:04:45,340
