66
00:04:45,460 --> 00:04:46,700
We always hang out with each other.

67
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:48,340
How did you hide that from me?

68
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:50,180
Chi,

69
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:51,460
it's okay if it's for your novel.

70
00:04:51,820 --> 00:04:53,220
Don't go too deep into this.

71
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:54,210
Don't get yourself crazy.

72
00:04:54,210 --> 00:04:56,500
Do you want me to take you to the hospital?

73
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:59,060
Let me put it this way.

74
00:05:00,220 --> 00:05:01,220
I feel that Xiao Xiu and I

75
00:05:02,810 --> 00:05:03,980
have known each other for a really long time.

76
00:05:04,980 --> 00:05:06,420
We know each other very well.

77
00:05:10,940 --> 00:05:11,930
So that's what you mean.

78
00:05:11,930 --> 00:05:12,740
I have been having

79
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:15,380
the same feeling recently.

80
00:05:18,420 --> 00:05:18,970
Get back to work.

81
00:05:27,060 --> 00:05:27,860
Chi Yan, Xiao Xiu.

82
00:05:28,420 --> 00:05:29,540
I just got off work.

83
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:31,180
Is there anything I can help with?

84
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:33,260
Xu Zihao just left.

85
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:34,260
Now you are here.

86
00:05:36,340 --> 00:05:37,690
We've almost finished.

87
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:39,010
We don't have much

88
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:41,340
left to be done.

89
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:43,260
We will move out in two days.

90
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:44,340
And we might need your help then.

91
00:05:44,580 --> 00:05:45,540
Please come and help us

92
00:05:45,980 --> 00:05:47,220
if you are available then.

93
00:05:48,060 --> 00:05:49,340
Xu Zihao would be here too.

94
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:52,330
Did he say anything to you?

95
00:05:52,330 --> 00:05:52,820
No.

96
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:53,500
Not much.

97
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:54,220
Absolutely nothing.

98
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:54,820
No.

99
00:05:56,380 --> 00:05:57,170
I mean,

100
00:05:57,610 --> 00:05:59,500
he and I have known each other since we were kids.

101
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:01,010
I know him very well.

102
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:03,100
It seems that he's always fooling around.

103
00:06:03,180 --> 00:06:03,770
But at the bottom of his heart,

104
00:06:03,770 --> 00:06:05,340
he's a very sincere guy.

105
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:07,780
We have our obstacles

106
00:06:07,780 --> 00:06:08,900
to overcome.

107
00:06:09,020 --> 00:06:09,820
He has his too.

108
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:14,820
He definitely said something to you.

109
00:06:16,970 --> 00:06:17,460
It's fine.

110
00:06:17,780 --> 00:06:18,700
See you in two days.

111
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:20,380
I need to get going now. Bye.

112
00:06:22,860 --> 00:06:23,500
Mingming, wait.

113
00:06:24,010 --> 00:06:24,740
I want to tell you something.

114
00:06:28,580 --> 00:06:29,500
How was your business trip?

115
00:06:29,730 --> 00:06:30,580
Fun?

116
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:32,340
It was fine.

117
00:06:33,740 --> 00:06:35,300
Why do you look so upset?

118
00:06:35,980 --> 00:06:37,060
Trouble at work?

119
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:39,420
Not really.

120
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:41,980
It's Mom.

121
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:44,100
You've got a girlfriend.

122
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:45,780
So she's targeting me now.

123
00:06:46,740 --> 00:06:48,220
I just got off the plane.

124
00:06:48,220 --> 00:06:49,740
She's already set up a blind date for me tonight.

125
00:06:50,020 --> 00:06:51,340
She said that if I don't go,

126
00:06:51,340 --> 00:06:52,940
it would break her heart.

127
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:54,100
This is so hard.

128
00:06:56,220 --> 00:06:57,740
Because you are free now.

129
00:06:58,100 --> 00:06:59,130
Who's the guy?

130
00:06:59,740 --> 00:07:00,620
Have you heard about him?

131
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:01,740
You know him.

132
00:07:01,980 --> 00:07:03,530
It's the doctor you introduced to Mom.

133
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:05,220
Doctor Luo.

134
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:07,930
Now I remember.

135
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:10,660
No wonder she called me to tell me off the other day.

136
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:11,980
She said that

137
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:13,530
if I know someone like that,

138
00:07:13,530 --> 00:07:14,940
I should have introduced him to you.

139
00:07:16,580 --> 00:07:17,490
It's a pity

140
00:07:17,740 --> 00:07:19,370
that she's not a salesperson.

141
00:07:20,660 --> 00:07:22,820
But Doctor Luo is indeed a decent guy.

142
00:07:23,220 --> 00:07:24,940
He should meet your standards.

143
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:27,500
Just try and see how things go.

144
00:07:53,020 --> 00:07:53,700
Luo.

145
00:07:53,810 --> 00:07:54,540
Chi Yan.

146
00:07:55,340 --> 00:07:56,820
What have you been up to these days?

147
00:07:58,260 --> 00:07:59,020
These days?

148
00:08:01,290 --> 00:08:02,260
I mean,

149
00:08:04,180 --> 00:08:05,020
long time no see.

150
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:07,340
How are you doing?

151
00:08:08,220 --> 00:08:09,980
Quite busy, as a doctor.

152
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:14,170
Good.

153
00:08:14,340 --> 00:08:15,020
How are you?

154
00:08:16,050 --> 00:08:16,980
I run this bookstore.

155
00:08:19,260 --> 00:08:19,780
So this is the thing.

156
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:21,700
My family set up a blind date for me the other day.

157
00:08:22,060 --> 00:08:22,820
I went and found that

158
00:08:22,820 --> 00:08:25,170
the girl was Xu Zihao's sister.

159
00:08:27,050 --> 00:08:27,620
Xu Ziqi.

160
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:28,180
Right.

161
00:08:28,690 --> 00:08:30,300
She told me that you run a bookstore here.

162
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:32,140
We haven't seen each other for a really long time,

163
00:08:32,140 --> 00:08:32,860
so I drop by to pay you a visit.

164
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:34,020
Right,

165
00:08:34,780 --> 00:08:35,740
this place

166
00:08:36,820 --> 00:08:38,220
is not easy to find.

167
00:08:38,780 --> 00:08:39,220
Right.

168
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:41,299
Seems that you are about to move.

169
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:42,780
They are tearing down this place.

170
00:08:43,380 --> 00:08:44,460
The landlord doesn't want to rent it to us.

171
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:46,820
Have you settled on a place?

172
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:47,780
Not yet.

173
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:49,930
We are trying to find one while packing.

174
00:08:59,140 --> 00:08:59,820
You have a cat.

175
00:09:04,300 --> 00:09:05,010
Thanks to you.

176
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:08,210
Thanks a lot for what happened, Luo.

177
00:09:09,530 --> 00:09:10,660
It's all history.

178
00:09:11,140 --> 00:09:12,340
It's good that you've recovered.

179
00:09:14,810 --> 00:09:15,690
Let me show you around.

180
00:09:16,340 --> 00:09:17,260
No, thanks.

181
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:18,580
I just want to see how you are doing.

182
00:09:18,770 --> 00:09:19,740
I need to get back to the hospital.

183
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:20,530
See you.

184
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:21,820
Let me walk you out.

185
00:09:23,260 --> 00:09:24,700
I will see if there are places for your bookstore.

186
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:26,220
Alright, thank you.

187
00:09:32,530 --> 00:09:33,100
Good.

188
00:09:38,210 --> 00:09:41,690
[Chi's Bookstore]

189
00:09:46,100 --> 00:09:46,700
Wait.

190
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:47,610
Please, wait.

191
00:09:47,610 --> 00:09:48,930
It's pretty fragile.

192
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:50,340
Save it for the last, alright?

193
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:51,700
Let's put it here first.

194
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:53,060
Careful.

195
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:56,730
Careful. Careful.

196
00:09:57,820 --> 00:09:58,930
Careful. Careful.

197
00:09:58,930 --> 00:09:59,740
Take a turn. Take a turn.

