[Chi's Bookstore]

199
00:10:23,810 --> 00:10:24,300
Careful.

200
00:10:31,220 --> 00:10:32,380
Nothing's left upstairs.

201
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:34,980
Thank you so much.

202
00:10:36,060 --> 00:10:36,500
No problem.

203
00:10:36,690 --> 00:10:38,060
The new place is almost ready.

204
00:10:38,330 --> 00:10:39,260
I will stay here.

205
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:40,580
You guys can leave first.

206
00:10:41,020 --> 00:10:41,580
Alright.

207
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:43,020
See you later then.

208
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:43,820
Let's go.

209
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:00,450
Let's go.

210
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:02,260
Just go back to the car and wait for me.

211
00:11:02,770 --> 00:11:04,020
I need to fetch something.

212
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:08,340
Be quick then.

