00:13:36,900 --> 00:13:38,100
Why are you looking at me?

236
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:39,500
What now?

237
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:41,260
I left a box at the old place.

238
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:43,330
That box is really important.

239
00:13:43,330 --> 00:13:44,580
And it's really heavy.

240
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:46,060
Could you help me take it here?

241
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:46,780
How heavy is that?

242
00:13:49,780 --> 00:13:51,340
Heavier than any box here.

243
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:55,210
What should we do?

244
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:56,140
It's so heavy.

245
00:13:56,140 --> 00:13:57,140
