246
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:58,580
Chi Yan and I are busy right now.

247
00:14:00,740 --> 00:14:01,780
What can we do?

248
00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:04,740
Mingming,

249
00:14:06,540 --> 00:14:07,970
can you help Xu Zihao?

250
00:14:14,780 --> 00:14:15,380
Sure.

251
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:17,060
I'll drive.

252
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:19,460
Good.

253
00:14:20,180 --> 00:14:20,580
You can go now.

254
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:21,620
Just go. I can take care of this.

255
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:48,060
You are too heavy.

256
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:50,270
Too heavy?

257
00:14:51,620 --> 00:14:52,380
Well.

258
00:14:53,700 --> 00:14:54,700
Let me get lighter.

259
00:15:23,690 --> 00:15:24,300
Hello.

260
00:15:29,730 --> 00:15:30,680
Hello.

261
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:38,860
Chi Yan.

262
00:15:40,660 --> 00:15:41,290
Luo.

263
00:15:41,290 --> 00:15:41,820
Welcome.

264
00:15:41,820 --> 00:15:42,580
Have a seat.

265
00:15:56,780 --> 00:15:57,980
Luo, you are too kind.

266
00:15:58,690 --> 00:15:59,450
Thank you.

267
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:00,890
You've moved to a place.

268
00:16:00,890 --> 00:16:02,460
Of course I need to come and congratulate you.

269
00:16:02,970 --> 00:16:04,660
A present for you. Have a look.

270
00:16:13,970 --> 00:16:14,920
Do you like it?

271
00:16:16,020 --> 00:16:16,660
Yes.

272
00:16:17,740 --> 00:16:18,610
Thank you.

273
00:16:21,860 --> 00:16:23,220
Let me help you set it up.

274
00:16:24,210 --> 00:16:24,820
Alright.

275
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:46,300
Those two are just mean,

276
00:16:47,330 --> 00:16:48,530
