277
00:16:51,730 --> 00:16:52,630
Wait.

278
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:53,860
Lift it up a little bit.

279
00:16:54,370 --> 00:16:54,980
Alright.

280
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:08,130
Now we can only carry it on our shoulders.

281
00:17:10,300 --> 00:17:10,770
Let's go.

282
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:14,290
Three, two, one, go.

283
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:17,369
I'll go first.

284
00:17:17,859 --> 00:17:18,619
You follow me.

285
00:17:19,010 --> 00:17:19,500
Steady.

286
00:17:20,140 --> 00:17:21,420
Slowly. Slowly.

287
00:17:23,380 --> 00:17:23,940
Careful.

288
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:41,780
My foot.

289
00:17:43,180 --> 00:17:43,700
The box.

